      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2011 BMW M3 (E92) in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a lightning-fast M-DCT dual-clutch transmission, the drivetrain is complemented by a factory variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing precise rebound and compression. Meticulously maintained with documented rod bearing and throttle actuator service, this vehicle exhibits zero subframe fatigue or fluid seepage. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior leather bolsters show no ingress wear. A mechanically flawless specimen for the discerning purist.",
